target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6169913&amp;page=8</a><br />\n16/12/2015 23:48 已有人唱-&gt; <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user1855258/2-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser1855258%2F2-1&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo58bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=813c2f4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user1855258/2-1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BO7LvQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBO7LvQ.png&h=16e25f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n// 苦苦堅持　經已沒意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n球迷不得意　而你卻責備誰　誰不公讓我身處榜尾位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歐冠下季冇著落時 輸波懺悔沒定時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情願你別來　炒這失勢女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n捧英超時　囂到沒法子　而如今失意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倫敦中只得我沒有救醫　球迷就算最愛我不過暫時fuck <br />\n名次每到六日都改變位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一變四　四變十二　來到這禮拜更加諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n＊何以　我變了你的十六位廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如若　碰上了記招摩佬會說錯判黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偶爾缺席　扮作受害人　能轉個化身自閉去度日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以前是冠轟　怎會慣　做落後廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經　也上到最高逐漸滑落谷底的暗 <br />\n看見未來　摩帥已在震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因我懺悔黑鳩阿狗　才會受教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謙卑的人　只要做亞軍　仍然很興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n誰知吞聲忍氣就變廢轟　人人話老細信你好過別人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連跌到尾五六七都會默允<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輸到尾　我太沒運　誰帶領也會痛失三分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/red] <br />\n<br />\nREPEAT ＊ <br />\n<br />\n不想再繼續　靠黑暗　我怕贏了惹公憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面對幾千個敵軍　只有疑問　為何隊隊亦要黑鳩我轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n期盼　那去屆冠軍續玩弄世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n誰料 碰上了李斯顯得我更廢似出殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最怕以後位置再下沉　前四也最好恨也再別恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以前是冠轟　怎會慣　十六弟見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經　也上過冠軍現在份外深深不忿fuck <br />\n我那後防　開賽已在震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我變了這樣隨便　唯有受教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  //"}]}